node.text:
2 days before the world shut down the 🐐 @lovehazelrenee put together the craziest surprise party, with the dopest theme, and the dopest people. I’ve held this video since March wondering when would be the right time to post it given the climate of the world. Well God dammit 2020 is coming to an end and now I want to share with y’all my dirty 30th! Shoutout to everybody who flewed in from all over the country to be with me on this day. RIP Deebo! Happy New Year! Cheers to an amazing 2021🥂

🎥: @chrisscholar

PSA: If you’re  not using @diannvalentine for your events you wasting tour time and money 🤷🏿‍♂️! Thank you, for bring this to life. MARTTTTIIINNNNNNN! I’M THE MAN!

Thank

node.text:
Today my first PE with @conversehoops is dropping and I couldn’t feel more proud. I came into this league believing I could be a player with their own PE and now, not only have I accomplished this, but I get to share it with my fans who will be able to purchase them too. 
 
Swarm your competition!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Draymond Green on April 22, 2021 tagging @livelarq. May be an image of 1 person and bottle.

node.text:
One of my goals is to be more environmentally conscious and having a reusable bottle that stays clean and odor-free while purifying my water when I'm traveling has saved me. A step in the right direction. 

I'm a proud partner with @livelarq because they give back to communities by participating in ocean plastic cleanup and supplying clean water to communities lacking access to clean water. This year, they've introduced carbon-neutral shipping & returns! 

In honor of #EarthDay 🌏, I want to give you a chance to experience the self-cleaning bottle too, so I'm giving away 5 of my limited collaboration LARQ Bottle DG23 Editions, signed by me.  

How to enter:
	1	Follow @livelarq 
	2	Like this post
	3	Tag a friend in the comments
	4	Bonus entries for sharing this post in your Stories! (Tag @livelarq to be counted!)

5 winners will be chosen at random and contacted via DM 
Giveaway closes 11:59PM PDT 4/23. Winners will be contacted by 4/26.
